title: Sensei to Ikenai H
sinopse:
A bad girl who seduced her teacher must be scolded… A slightly changed Sensei, a cool adult Sensei, and an older, yet cute Sensei… Nobody will refuse to have a Love & H with these Sensei.

1-2) Baby, Baby (Takahashi Yuu) 3) Higurashi Naku Yuugure Ni (Saionji Michiru) 4) Love & Peach (Ashika Nozomu) 5) Sweet Teacher (Earithen) 6) Ai wo Hore! (Koishikawa Funi)
